Account Microservice

The Account Microservice provides account information based on the account number passed in the URL.

Endpoint

GET /accounts/{number}

Example Request

http://localhost:8080/accounts/00987987973432

Sample Response

{
  "number": "00987987973432",
  "type": "Savings",
  "balance": 234343.0
}
Loan Microservice

The Loan Microservice provides loan details for a given loan account number.

Endpoint

GET /loans/{number}

Example Request

http://localhost:8081/loans/H00987987972342

Sample Response

{
  "number": "H00987987972342",
  "type": "car",
  "loan": 400000,
  "emi": 3258,
  "tenure": 18
}
